1
00:00:29,170 --> 00:00:30,090
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#2d1508">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A faint flower was blooming 
unnoticed by anyone</i></font>

3
00:00:35,490 --> 00:00:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a burning red, 
but flickering serenely in red</i></font>

4
00:00:40,490 --> 00:00:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been pausing for a long time 
dragging my past at my feet</i></font>

5
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I break free from this ambivalence,</i></font>

6
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>will I be able to bloom by its side?</i></font>

7
00:00:51,850 --> 00:00:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The future is slipping away 
between my fingers</i></font>

8
00:00:54,490 --> 00:00:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What mistake did I make 
to pay this price?</i></font>

9
00:00:57,010 --> 00:01:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always hurting myself</i></font>

10
00:01:01,860 --> 00:01:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and hesitant even to a small joy</i></font>

11
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stop now</i></font>

12
00:01:09,410 --> 00:01:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The flower just bloomed in dignity</i></font>

13
00:01:11,930 --> 00:01:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that was all I needed to be happy</i></font>

14
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanted to protect this one flower</i></font>

15
00:01:19,670 --> 00:01:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wishing to be strong, I</i></font>

16
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>picked up the vulnerability 
I had once cast away</i></font>

17
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can't break free from the ambivalence</i></font>

18
00:01:26,990 --> 00:01:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In ambivalence, I become myself</i></font>

19
00:01:30,180 --> 00:01:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like rooting strongly into the soil</i></font>

20
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>like swaying ephemerally to the wind</i></font>

21
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm slowly loosening myself to bloom</i></font>

22
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:41,660
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></b></font>

23
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:50,460
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>Love and Karma</b></font>

24
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, support my brother.</font>

25
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw that. I'm taking 
the monster's head.</font>

26
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't kill the Tensen.</font>

27
00:01:56,510 --> 00:01:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that! It's an expression!</font>

28
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just do as my brother says!</font>

29
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, man-woman!</font>

30
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiots.</font>

31
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay back, idiots.</font>

32
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm stuck defending.</i></font>

33
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother!</font>

34
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said stay back!</font>

35
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't block all 
the tentacles and spores.</i></font>

36
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

37
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When they're combined, 
they attack twice as much.</i></font>

38
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The runt and old guy suck at using tao.</i></font>

39
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Toma's tao won't hinder them.</i></font>

40
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But my tao hinders Tao Fa's, 
and I've got something in mind for Ju Fa.</i></font>

41
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the only one 
who can kill the monster.</i></font>

42
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the case of water tao,</font>

43
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">objects containing it, such as chestnuts, 
soybeans, kidneys, or bladders,</font>

44
00:02:58,470 --> 00:03:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can be gathered and fermented 
to produce tao-infused spirits.</font>

45
00:03:03,170 --> 00:03:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Write the subject's name 
on a perfumed talisman.</font>

46
00:03:07,540 --> 00:03:11,300
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#aa191b">Yamada Asaemon Toma</font></b></font>

47
00:03:07,540 --> 00:03:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tao-rich catalysts will resonate,</font>

48
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">allowing you to see the target's 
fortune and current state.</font>

49
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chobe.</font>

50
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:19,550
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#aa191b">Yamada Asaemon Toma</font></b></font>

51
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your brother's future bears an ill omen.</font>

52
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll do it alone.</i></font>

53
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I always have. It's not a problem.</i></font>

54
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Livestock.</font>

55
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you.</font>

56
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Brother?</font>

57
00:03:56,170 --> 00:03:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

58
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This had better work.</font>

59
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will.</font>

60
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

61
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By strengthening my metal with your 
earth, we can hinder Tao Fa's tao.</font>

62
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So even two males are effective together.</font>

63
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems that way. Let's press them.</font>

64
00:04:25,910 --> 00:04:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to kill that monster!</font>

65
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Piece of shit!</font>

66
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the piece of shit!</font>

67
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said I'd kill the monster!</font>

68
00:04:38,770 --> 00:04:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay out of our way!</font>

69
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your wounds will open if they get wet.</font>

70
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be fine, idiot.</font>

71
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brother told us 
to stay back, so stay back.</font>

72
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I never even saw him argue 
back when we were bandits.</i></font>

73
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All he ever did was copy me.</i></font>

74
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look up, idiots.</font>

75
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

76
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They turned inside out?</font>

77
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're switching 
from attacking to defending.</font>

78
00:05:43,450 --> 00:05:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're letting their injured half rest.</font>

79
00:05:46,450 --> 00:05:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cutting that will get us nowhere.</font>

80
00:05:48,550 --> 00:05:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to destroy Ju Fa and 
Tao Fa's tanden at the same time.</font>

81
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me, old man.</font>

82
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

83
00:05:56,330 --> 00:06:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll split up. 
Together, we'll kill Ju Fa.</font>

84
00:06:00,990 --> 00:06:02,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a plan.</font>

85
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys kill Tao Fa.</font>

86
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The method you used earlier should work.</font>

87
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well, Brother.</font>

88
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly should we—</font>

89
00:06:12,490 --> 00:06:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ask too many questions.</font>

90
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow. That hurts, Brother.</font>

91
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving it all up to you.</font>

92
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use your own head.</font>

93
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do that now, can't you?</font>

94
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need any direction.</font>

95
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you, you know.</font>

96
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My plan won't work without the skills of 
the man unparalleled in eight provinces.</font>

97
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, in that case...</font>

98
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the face my brother makes 
when he commands subordinates.</i></font>

99
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're desperate to defend yourselves.</font>

100
00:07:02,590 --> 00:07:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have some sympathy for that.</font>

101
00:07:05,010 --> 00:07:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they've grown more than you realize.</font>

102
00:07:08,610 --> 00:07:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you remain in that embrace, 
you'll crush each other to death.</font>

103
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll cut you apart.</font>

104
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that what you want? 
To die together?</font>

105
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother!</font>

106
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're reacting 
to all four of us at once.</i></font>

107
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no opportunity 
to attack their tanden.</i></font>

108
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little guy and man-woman, back me up!</font>

109
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

110
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll create an opening for you!</font>

111
00:07:47,910 --> 00:07:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you intend to do?</font>

112
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know, but let's trust him.</font>

113
00:08:03,170 --> 00:08:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gantetsusai!</font>

114
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine. Let's keep going!</font>

115
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way he's fine.</i></font>

116
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's just acting tough.</i></font>

117
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Countless lacerations and 
contusions. Organ damage.</i></font>

118
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The back-to-back fights 
have him nearing his limit.</i></font>

119
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toma!</font>

120
00:08:36,530 --> 00:08:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your tao is the key to my brother's plan.</font>

121
00:08:39,420 --> 00:08:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get it together.</font>

122
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-Forgive me.</font>

123
00:08:41,940 --> 00:08:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it. Let's go!</font>

124
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're all covered in wounds.</i></font>

125
00:08:52,010 --> 00:08:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if we miss this chance...</i></font>

126
00:08:53,980 --> 00:08:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We cannot win.</i></font>

127
00:08:59,930 --> 00:09:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's ready, brats.</font>

128
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gatecleaver Strike!</font>

129
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're regenerating! 
Don't miss this chance, Toma!</font>

130
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is Tao Fa's tanden?</font>

131
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bottom right! Direction of the dog!</font>

132
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa!</font>

133
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more. Enough.</font>

134
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao Fa!</font>

135
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're still not dead?</font>

136
00:10:21,810 --> 00:10:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't hinder them.</font>

137
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To kill them, we have to 
stop their regeneration</font>

138
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">after destroying their tanden.</font>

139
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother?!</font>

140
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My secret weapon.</font>

141
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd actually planned to use this 
to kill the little fire shinobi.</font>

142
00:10:49,490 --> 00:10:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you can have it.</font>

143
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the tao-infused spirits they use.</font>

144
00:10:58,300 --> 00:11:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured I'd swipe their water tao.</font>

145
00:11:03,310 --> 00:11:06,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And my gut's never wrong.</font>

146
00:11:08,810 --> 00:11:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's working immediately.</font>

147
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hindering effect is 
preventing you from regenerating.</font>

148
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You spilled everything you knew 
about hindering and tao.</font>

149
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you really think I'd changed sides?</font>

150
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serves you right.</font>

151
00:11:24,770 --> 00:11:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll die regretting picking a fight 
with me and my brother.</font>

152
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How distasteful.</font>

153
00:11:32,570 --> 00:11:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Distasteful?</font>

154
00:11:34,090 --> 00:11:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brother is a supremely wicked man.</font>

155
00:11:42,370 --> 00:11:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't kill them.</font>

156
00:11:44,770 --> 00:11:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you feel sorry for them, old man?</font>

157
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said I'd be the one 
to finish off the monster.</font>

158
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't fun for me at all.</font>

159
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had fun, miss.</font>

160
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Tao Fa. I... I...</font>

161
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't protect you.</font>

162
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

163
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao Fa...</font>

164
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I was paired with you, Ju Fa.</font>

165
00:12:43,410 --> 00:12:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't believe we all survived.</i></font>

166
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are the others all right?</font>

167
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:55,550
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}Several Moments Earlier</b></font>

168
00:12:56,880 --> 00:13:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, let me say 
I don't intend to fight you.</font>

169
00:13:01,850 --> 00:13:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just told to stay here by myself.</font>

170
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if you don't bother me, 
I won't bother you.</font>

171
00:13:12,170 --> 00:13:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you do, I'll crush you.</font>

172
00:13:20,650 --> 00:13:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is that? They're reading a book?</i></font>

173
00:13:23,570 --> 00:13:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No doubt. This is rentan palace.</font>

174
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Rien not here.</font>

175
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is Rien, Gui Fa?</font>

176
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rien left just now.</font>

177
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just told to look after this.</font>

178
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"This"?</font>

179
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gui Fa very shy. Even more than before.</font>

180
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:57,360
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#b62925">Yamada Asaemon Shion
Nurugai</font></b></font>

181
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is Rite of Clarity.</font>

182
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Objects containing tao turned into 
catalysts to see fate and fortune.</font>

183
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use talismans to see target.</font>

184
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We knew you would come.</font>

185
00:14:03,970 --> 00:14:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been waiting here for you.</font>

186
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then if we destroy that, they won't 
be able to read our movements.</font>

187
00:14:14,370 --> 00:14:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this a tao attack from above?</i></font>

188
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I'm being crushed.</i></font>

189
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take your hand off your sword.</font>

190
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sagiri!</font>

191
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can still move? Impressive.</font>

192
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have orders from Rien.</font>

193
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to fight, I'll crush you.</font>

194
00:14:39,730 --> 00:14:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't intend to fight.</font>

195
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, allow me to apologize.</font>

196
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:50,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For invading your island, 
and everything we've done since.</font>

197
00:14:50,740 --> 00:14:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We may have been ignorant, 
but we are to blame.</font>

198
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I apologize for that.</font>

199
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sagiri...</font>

200
00:14:58,350 --> 00:14:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How commendable.</font>

201
00:15:00,310 --> 00:15:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I've also seen things 
that make my blood boil.</font>

202
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you're the ones who 
lured humans to this island.</font>

203
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, you brought 
this conflict upon yourselves.</font>

204
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't you think both sides have lost 
too much to simply write this off as that?</font>

205
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I came to stop the fighting.</font>

206
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:26,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pointless for us to 
continue killing each other.</font>

207
00:15:27,010 --> 00:15:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will leave the island without a word.</font>

208
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ask that you let us go.</font>

209
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Elixir and shogunate 
aren't the priority now.</i></font>

210
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Making it back alive comes first.</i></font>

211
00:15:39,170 --> 00:15:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her tao has risen. This woman...</i></font>

212
00:15:45,830 --> 00:15:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The pressure vanished.</i></font>

213
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. I'll let you go.</font>

214
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was only told to protect this place.</font>

215
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was never really interested in this.</font>

216
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

217
00:15:56,160 --> 00:16:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't think there's a point 
in returning to Wakoku alive anymore.</font>

218
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

219
00:16:05,690 --> 00:16:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You asked where Rien went, Mei.</font>

220
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

221
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm showing you 
a tao illusion, not reality.</font>

222
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rien is beneath the main palace.</font>

223
00:16:22,710 --> 00:16:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They went to the sluice gate.</font>

224
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're preparing a ship with the doshi.</font>

225
00:16:29,090 --> 00:16:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ship? For what purpose?</font>

226
00:16:36,850 --> 00:16:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To turn all the humans of Wakoku into tan.</font>

227
00:16:40,230 --> 00:16:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? How?</font>

228
00:16:42,410 --> 00:16:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The completed starter has been 
embedded in paradise butterflies</font>

229
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and packed onto a ship.</font>

230
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll emerge in Wakoku</font>

231
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and disperse.</font>

232
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thousands of butterflies capable 
of flying vast distances.</font>

233
00:17:36,390 --> 00:17:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the blink of an eye, 
they'll envelop Wakoku.</font>

234
00:17:51,260 --> 00:17:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the humans have 
become Waitanhua Flowers,</font>

235
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they'll come together as one.</font>

236
00:17:57,650 --> 00:18:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll become Banko, the god beast, 
and refine the perfect tan Rien seeks.</font>

237
00:18:09,730 --> 00:18:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sagiri!</font>

238
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's pointless to return. 
You'd just turn into flowers.</font>

239
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

240
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do all of this?</font>

241
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

242
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

243
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think we'll understand each other 
if we discuss the reason?</font>

244
00:18:37,190 --> 00:18:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what you know about us, 
but you're barking up the wrong tree.</font>

245
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans are merely 
an ingredient for the Elixir.</font>

246
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have no more attachment for you 
than we would for critters.</font>

247
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not true.</font>

248
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandmaster's research 
for emperor and people.</font>

249
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know using human life wrong.</font>

250
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The situation has changed, Mei.</font>

251
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We tried scattering chum several times.</font>

252
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few hundred years ago, 
the first outsiders came to the island.</font>

253
00:19:12,670 --> 00:19:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's when we learned...</font>

254
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how marvelous humans are.</font>

255
00:19:20,930 --> 00:19:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their fragility and 
the quality of their tao</font>

256
00:19:23,910 --> 00:19:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were greater than we expected.</font>

257
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were a far better 
ingredient than the Hoko.</font>

258
00:19:35,570 --> 00:19:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ran was drawn to their beauty.</font>

259
00:19:38,570 --> 00:19:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mu Dan seemed to enjoy themselves, too.</font>

260
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa and Tao Fa also realized</font>

261
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that using humans was 
the quickest way to end our training.</font>

262
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans are full of doubt.</font>

263
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doubt is the essence of tao.</font>

264
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They waver between two extremes.</font>

265
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is what makes humans so fantastic.</font>

266
00:19:57,800 --> 00:19:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love and hate.</font>

267
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Life and death.</font>

268
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We Tensen know neither love nor death.</font>

269
00:20:04,470 --> 00:20:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Searching for a different ingredient 
now would be unthinkable.</font>

270
00:20:10,020 --> 00:20:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially now that 
the Elixir has been perfected.</font>

271
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impossible for us 
to reach an understanding.</font>

272
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind letting you go, 
but a truce would be pointless.</font>

273
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we can do now is take from each other.</font>

274
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While we're speaking...</font>

275
00:20:33,380 --> 00:20:35,880
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#a21f20">Yamada Asaemon Shion</font></b></font>

276
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">another will be taken.</font>

277
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:51,650
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#a21f20">Yamada Asaemon Shion</font></b></font>

278
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nurugai.</font>

279
00:20:52,300 --> 00:20:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many is that?</font>

280
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:56,280
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#2d1416">Yamada Asaemon Shion</font></b></font>

281
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:56,280
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#a21f20">Yamada Asaemon Shion</font></b></font>

282
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, two...</font>

283
00:20:59,910 --> 00:21:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two hundred fifteen...</font>

284
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've cut them 215 times.</font>

285
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've killed them 215 times.</font>

286
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their regeneration is slowing.</i></font>

287
00:21:15,180 --> 00:21:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just like we discussed.</i></font>

288
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't kill your opponent 
without hindering tao.</font>

289
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But is that the only way 
to overpower the Tensen?</font>

290
00:21:26,430 --> 00:21:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about exhausting them 
through regeneration?</font>

291
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When done in rapid succession, 
it seems to slow down.</font>

292
00:21:33,130 --> 00:21:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exhausting tao for regeneration 
probably impossible.</font>

293
00:21:36,690 --> 00:21:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can regenerate hundred, thousand times.</font>

294
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill someone a thousand times? 
With a magic trick?</font>

295
00:21:44,650 --> 00:21:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called tao.</font>

296
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd be impossible for an ordinary man.</font>

297
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, you can't keep going!</font>

298
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did we say a thousand times?</font>

299
00:22:05,010 --> 00:22:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like it'll take fewer than that.</font>

300
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

301
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Nurugai!</font>

302
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go after them.</font>

303
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're exhausted as well. 
They won't recover right away.</font>

304
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll finish them 
carefully and decisively.</font>

305
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with you? You're insane.</font>

306
00:22:47,010 --> 00:22:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who takes cannot understand.</font>

307
00:22:49,970 --> 00:22:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But their victim never forgets.</font>

308
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:14,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the other side, even today</i></font>

309
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone is unraveling, 
yet they still stand</i></font>

310
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A stab to the chest, this loneliness</i></font>

311
00:23:26,010 --> 00:23:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Points and lines, 
breaking off and vanishing</i></font>

312
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My shattered mask</i></font>

313
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's more than I can bear</i></font>

314
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I must keep on living</i></font>

315
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow awaits to greet me</i></font>

316
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's endless</i></font>

317
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so fragile</i></font>

318
00:23:51,130 --> 00:23:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it better to believe 
hearts don't exist at all?</i></font>

319
00:23:57,360 --> 00:24:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Radiant and soft</i></font>

320
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was the hand</i></font>

321
00:24:04,630 --> 00:24:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I squeezed back on that day</i></font>

